# Alert — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/alert.css`

## Architecture

ALL styling in CSS via `@apply` + raw CSS. React only composes class names via `clsx`. Inline SVGs for default icons (no lucide-react).

## CSS Classes

### Base
`.acko-alert` — `@apply flex items-center gap-3 relative w-full`, padding `var(--space-3)` (12px) all sides, border-radius `--radius-3xl`, border 1px solid

### Variants

| Class | Background | Border | Text |
|-------|------------|--------|------|
| `.acko-alert-info` | `--color-info-subtle` | `--color-info-border` | `--color-info-text` |
| `.acko-alert-success` | `--color-success-subtle` | `--color-success-border` | `--color-success-text` |
| `.acko-alert-warning` | `--color-warning-subtle` | `--color-warning-border` | `--color-warning-text` |
| `.acko-alert-error` | `--color-error-subtle` | `--color-error-border` | `--color-error-text` |

Icon and title use variant text color (e.g. `--color-info-text`).

> **Note:** Info variant uses **purple** (brand color), not blue. The `--color-info-*` tokens map to purple primitives.

### Children
- `.acko-alert-icon` — `--scale-20` size, color inherited from variant, vertically centered
- `.acko-alert-content` — flex-1, flex flex-col gap-0, `min-width: 0` (title + subtitle tight)
- `.acko-alert-title` — `body-sm` size, font-weight 600, truncate
- `.acko-alert-body` — `caption` size, color `--color-text-default`, truncate
- `.acko-alert-dismiss` — inline centered (not absolute positioned), `--scale-20` size, opacity 0.7, hover opacity 1

### Animation
`acko-alert-slide-up` — 300ms `var(--ease-out-cubic)` from bottom: `translateY(8px) → 0`

## Dark Theme

Automatic via semantic token remapping. All `--color-{variant}-subtle`, `--color-{variant}-border`, `--color-{variant}-text`, and `--color-text-default` tokens remap to dark values in `tokens.css`.
